nodes.text: Qiaxx was a planet in the Cor'ric sector of the Outer Rim Territories.
Qiaxx was the base of operations for Dequc's Black Sun splinter group Black Nebula. It was the site of an elaborate casino—owned by Dequc via intermediaries—and the famous Bubble Cliffs of Nezmi.
Emperor's Hand Mara Jade traveled to the planet in order to eliminate Dequc several months after the Battle of Endor.
